Code to reproduce the analyses of the AWST paper: Analysis of the LGG data
Figure 19 and 20.

S.M.Pagnotta - Dept. of Science and Technology, Universita’ degli Studi del Sannio (Benevento, Italy)
D.Risso - Dept. of Statistical Sciences, Universita’ degli Studi di Padova (Padova, Italy)

compiled on dicembre 28, 2020

Here we show the code to reproduce the analyses of: Risso and Pagnotta (2020). Per-sample standardization and asymmetric winsorization lead to accurate classification of RNA-seq expression profiles. In preparation.

This file belongs to the repository: https://github.com/drisso/awst_analysis.

The code is released with license GPL v3.0.

In this script we analyze LGG data normalized with transformation of Townes et al. (2019).
